This paper deals with multi-agent networked dynamic systems and optimization of their objectives. The paper specifically focuses on the application of these concepts to the wide-area control of power systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
